<DOCID> 002894 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 11, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
