<P>
63 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY: COMPANY TOWN ANNEX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 IMAX and Douglas Trumbull Firm to Merge: The Massachusetts company headed by 
Trumbull, who worked on special effects for films such as "2001: A Space 
Odyssey" and "Close Encounters of the Third Kind" will be combined with IMAX 
using a new holding company, WGIM Acquisitions Corp. IMAX, based in Canada, is 
best known for developing a large-screen format for showing films. 
</P>
</TEXT>
