</P>
<P>
 * Converse: A new line of shoes to be introduced by "Grandmama" hoopster Larry 
Johnson. 
</P>
<P>
 * McDonald's: Two NFL field goal kickers square off in an exaggerated 
competition. 
</P>
<P>
 * Frito-Lay: An ad introducing Wavy Lay's potato chips and Chevy Chase for 
Doritos. 
</P>
<P>
 * Pepsi: Several flashy, new ads to promote Pepsi and Diet Pepsi brands. 
</P>
<P>
 * Master Lock: One ad promoting durability of lock. 
</P>
<P>
 * 7-Up: The animated 7-Up "spot" returns for another adventure. 
</P>
