<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEW VISION FOR THE OLD WORLD; SUMMIT AT A GLANCE; MONDAY'S ACCOMPLISHMENTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 President Clinton and other NATO leaders invited their former Warsaw Pact 
rivals to become limited partners in the Western military alliance. 
</P>
<P>
 A deal negotiated by U.S. officials with Russia and Ukraine will dismantle 
Ukraine's nuclear arsenal, the third largest in the world. 
</P>
<P>
