money will be used to finance two new restaurants, in Coconut Grove, Fla., and 
Bethesda, Md., later this summer. It will also be used to build a new corporate 
headquarters and bakery. Cheesecake owns eight restaurants. They are in 
Southern California, Atlanta and Washington, D. C. 
